      <div class="msgContentFrame">She walks in Beauty <br /> <br />--Talk to the left NPC at the gold guild <br />--Talk to Colbernaux inside the instance at the Gold guild <br />--Run up to Nanawa Mines entrance and speak with Z'ssapa <br />--Back to Colbernaux <br />--Head over to the miners guild and talk/parley with the 3 miners (disgruntled miner etc, forget the others names) <br />--Head back to Colbernaux and synth the brooch (I nearly busted it with the lvl 12 hammer naked so may want support etc) <br />--Talk to Colbernaux <br />--Talk to the mithra that shows up and use the power of the echo <br />--Talk to starting npc at the gold guild <br /> <br /> <br />Didn't see it anywhere so this is the basic rundown.  Death warping from nanawa maybe 10-15 minutes all told.  Dunno what happens if you bust the synth but if I know SE you get to collect the ingredients from nanawa/miners guild again.<div class="msgSig"><div class="msgSigBar sm">----------------------------</div> <br /> <br /></div></div>
